changeAdmin.description: Changes the admin of the contract to the new address.

upgradeTo.description: Upgrades the contract to a new implementation address.

upgradeToAndCall.description: Upgrades the contract to a new implementation address and executes the provided data.

admin.description: Returns the current admin of the contract.

implementation.description: Returns the current implementation address of the contract.

AdminChanged.description: Emitted when the admin of the contract is changed.

BeaconUpgraded.description: Emitted when the beacon address is upgraded.

Upgraded.description: Emitted when the implementation address is upgraded.

constructor.description: Initializes the contract with the logic address, admin address, and optional initialization data.

fallback.description: Fallback function to handle calls that don't match any other function signature.

receive.description: Receive function to handle incoming Ether transfers.
